WrongTimeFormat:
The format used for time is not recognized by the application.
The WMS standard supports 4 ways of adding dates inside a WMS, which are:
	A single date;
	Multiple dates comma separated;
	Start/End/Interval;
	Start1/End1/Interval1,Start2/End2/Interval2,etc.
If you wish to add this layer to AniMet, you will need to update the WMS source accordingly.
